content: I want to analyze Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, and TikTok. My content categories are pretty basic, like vlogs, educational, promotional, and behind-the-scenes. I'm interested in engagement rate, likes, comments, and followers gained. I want to focus on the last month. I have access to analytics tools on each platform. By the way, I noticed my Instagram followers have been growing rapidly, especially in the last month - I think I gained around 150 followers.
